---
title: European-Style Beef Meatballs and Cavatappi with Mushroom Sauce and Spinach
description: Inspired by a classic beef stroganoff, this is anything but your average meatball recipe. Juicy beef meatballs are simmered in a lush and creamy sauce spiked with tangy cream cheese. Discover why these flavours are so beloved!
